686a209d2042c63fb3d090bf1850a55a58a02863.query:
UPDATE withdrawals
        SET verified_in_block=$1
        WHERE block_number >= $2 AND block_number <= $3

732df0c45d86aa9b015cf06fe890abf446d4a2bc.query:

        SET executed_in_block=$1
        WHERE block_number >= $2 AND block_number <= $3

842d82d56729ddcd0a3216e6dee5406148a0fc86.query:
UPDATE withdrawals
        SET committed_in_block=$1
        WHERE block_number >= $2 AND block_number <= $3

96006f4ea4cdd22b986a0cf64e40ea40750c7505.query:
INSERT INTO committed_l1_events
        (
            l1_block_number,
            l1_batch_number,
            l2_range_begin,
            l2_range_end
        )
        VALUES ( $1, $2, $3, $4 )
        ON CONFLICT (l1_block_number) DO NOTHING

c3dd8ecc5a2e38f5d615b6d4f319b904307a7b91.query:
INSERT INTO withdrawals
        (
            tx_hash,
            block_number,
            token,
            amount,
            event_index_in_tx,
            committed_in_block,
            verified_in_block,
            executed_in_block
        )
        VALUES (
            $1, $2, $3, $4, $5,
            (
                SELECT l1_block_number
                FROM committed_l1_events
                WHERE l2_range_begin <= $2 AND l2_range_end >= $2
            ),
            (
                SELECT l1_block_number
                FROM verified_l1_events
                WHERE l2_range_begin <= $2 AND l2_range_end >= $2
            ),
            (
                SELECT l1_block_number
                FROM executed_l1_events
                WHERE l2_range_begin <= $2 AND l2_range_end >= $2
            )
        )
        ON CONFLICT (tx_hash, event_index_in_tx) DO NOTHING
